Size&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:800,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:430573,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff475f985-1965-44f6-9d8f-f7dfa35ecd98_1200x800.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff475f985-1965-44f6-9d8f-f7dfa35ecd98_1200x800.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff475f985-1965-44f6-9d8f-f7dfa35ecd98_1200x800.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff475f985-1965-44f6-9d8f-f7dfa35ecd98_1200x800.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></figure></div><p>我刚刚参加完<a href="http://kilkenomics.com/">基尔肯经济学节</a>，这是在爱尔兰小城基尔肯尼举行的一年一度的节日。基尔肯经济学是一个相当独特的活动，爱尔兰喜剧演员就各种话题采访外国经济学家和经济评论员。我的采访主要是关于战争和不断变化的全球秩序——这些都是当今很多人脑海中浮现的严峻话题。在这种情况下，我试图让事情尽可能轻松，主要是通过取笑英国人。总而言之，这是我强烈推荐的一次体验。</p><p>但我在基尔肯尼的逗留让我明白了一个事实，我在理智上知道这一点，但从未在内心体验过：爱尔兰是一个极其富裕的国家。基尔肯尼的小市中心和我在欧洲去过的任何地方一样好，就像奥斯陆、苏黎世或阿姆斯特丹的一小部分——几个街区的小商店、咖啡馆、餐馆、酒吧和百货商店，还有一座古老的城堡和一些大教堂在市中心之外，景观很快转变为以汽车为中心的美式风格单户住宅，分布在连绵起伏的绿色田野中。</p><p>这不是我小时候想象的爱尔兰的样子。我脑海中对这个国家的想象总是贫穷和冲突——马铃薯饥荒、1800年代身无分文的移民涌入美国海岸、乔纳森·斯威夫特的讽刺作品、詹姆斯·乔伊斯的小说、麻烦等等。就在 1991 年，这种刻板印象仍然有一定道理——爱尔兰的人均 GDP 低于西欧大多数其他国家。但奇迹般的16年后，情况发生了逆转： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg" width="1020" height="728" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:728,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:111929,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Ireland's capital is Dublin every year!&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="Ireland's capital is Dublin every year!" title="每年爱尔兰的首都都是都柏林！" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>当然，您可能听说爱尔兰的国内生产总值被严重夸大了。确实如此——现在。上图结束于 2007 年是有充分理由的；如果你看一下爱尔兰<a href="https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/gdp-per-capita-worldbank?tab=chart&amp;country=USA~DEU~GBR~FRA~KOR~JPN~CHN~IND~IRL">最近的 GDP 图表</a>，你会发现它飙升至荒谬的高度——人均超过 10 万美元。国家虽然富裕，但并不<em>富裕</em>。</p><p> 《经济学人》 <a href="https://www.economist.com/the-economist-explains/2023/10/31/whats-weird-about-irelands-gdp">最近的一篇文章</a>解释了正在发生的事情。爱尔兰的 GDP 被高估有两个主要原因。首先，也是最重要的一点，爱尔兰是著名的避税天堂——其较低的企业所得税税率使跨国公司有动力将尽可能多的利润记入其爱尔兰子公司。对于欧洲公司来说，这通常需要将他们的活动转移到爱尔兰，但美国有一个奇怪的公司税收制度， <a href="https://www.irishtimes.com/business/economy/explainer-google-and-its-double-irish-tax-scheme-1.4128929">允许谷歌和苹果等公司</a><a href="https://www.cfr.org/blog/apples-exports-arent-missing-they-are-ireland">参与</a>各种<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Double_Irish_arrangement">其他计划，</a> <a href="https://static1.squarespace.com/static/562636cfe4b043d43a7492bf/t/58dd39ae2e69cfde1f646716/1490893232477/ProfitShifting.pdf">在爱尔兰登记利润</a>，而无需在该国实际做任何实质性的事情，爱尔兰的国内生产总值膨胀。第二个奇怪的地方是飞机租赁，其统计处理没有多大意义。</p><p>为了停止夸大国内生产总值，爱尔兰实施了一种称为 GNI* 的特殊统计系统，即修正后的国民总收入。爱尔兰的国民总收入* 略高于其国内生产总值的一半。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg" width="688" height="458.6666666666667" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:800,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:688,&quot;bytes&quot;:77800,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：爱尔兰<a href="https://www.cso.ie/en/releasesandpublications/ep/p-ana/annualnationalaccounts2022/gniandde-globalisedresults/">中央统计局</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>但即使如此巨大的调整也意味着爱尔兰仍然相当富裕。它有 500 万人口，因此人均 GNI* 约为 54,000 美元，比英国的人均 GDP 高出约 16%，也高于德国或法国。</p><p>正如<a href="https://www.economist.com/the-economist-explains/2023/10/31/whats-weird-about-irelands-gdp">《经济学人》所表明的那样</a>，GNI* 直到 2000 年才真正开始与 GDP 出现背离，即使在 2007 年，这种背离也相当小。 20 世纪 90 年代和 2000 年代初爱尔兰经济的惊人增长是真实存在的。尽管2008年房地产泡沫破裂给爱尔兰带来了<a href="https://worksinprogress.co/issue/why-irelands-housing-bubble-burst">严重</a>打击，但爱尔兰仍然保持着世界上最富有经济体之一的地位。这个国家可能不再是“凯尔特之虎”，但它在那个辉煌时代所取得的成就似乎是安全的。</p><p>爱尔兰也是一个小型精英国家俱乐部的一部分，该俱乐部比其 19 世纪的帝国霸主还要富有，其他国家还有韩国、波兰、波罗的海国家和其他一些国家。现在轮到英国成为破旧、功能失调的表亲了。</p><p>我写了很多关于波兰的文章，每个人都读过关于韩国的文章。但爱尔兰是如何做到的呢？其他国家可以复制这一壮举吗？显然，我们永远不可能确切地知道一个国家为何变得富裕，但回顾历史，我们可以拼凑出一个看似合理的故事。</p><h4>爱尔兰是高科技出口强国</h4><p>我喜欢通过询问每家公司的专业领域来开始这些帖子。弄清楚这一点的一个好方法是查看出口。爱尔兰的出口主要集中在生物医学和制药行业，以及一些高科技电子制造业： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3dfb9e3-879b-4105-b838-da367a52e29b_722x661.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3dfb9e3-879b-4105-b838-da367a52e29b_722x661.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages