e><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>换句话说，凯尔特之虎看起来很像亚洲四小龙——一个生产大量高科技产品并将其销往世界其他地区的国家。当然，一个国家无法仅靠出口制造业生存——需要有强劲的当地经济来流通和<a href="https://eml.berkeley.edu/~moretti/multipliers.pdf">倍增</a>出口收入的收益。但出于多种原因，出口制造业是有用的。制造业本质上往往具有快速的生产率增长。许多人认为，出口还可以通过迫使本地公司在全球市场上竞争并帮助他们吸收外国技术来<a href="https://www.imf.org/en/Publications/WP/Issues/2019/03/26/The-Return-of-the-Policy-That-Shall-Not-Be-Named-Principles-of-Industrial-Policy-46710">提高生产率</a>。</p><p>爱尔兰能够实现这一目标的原因之一是其与美国和欧洲这两个重要经济体的特殊关系。</p><h4>来自美国的投资，欧洲市场</h4><p>如果您想大量出口，您需要有地方销售您的产品。爱尔兰的出口目的地实际上非常多元化： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg" width="636" height="586.6703601108034" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:666,&quot;width&quot;:722,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:636,&quot;bytes&quot;:130828,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">来源： <a href="https://oec.world/en/profile/country/irl?yearSelector1=2021">OEC</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>欧洲显然是这里最大的，这并不奇怪，因为地理位置很接近。但爱尔兰是欧盟的一部分——而且在此之前是欧洲经济共同体的一部分——这一事实肯定会有所帮助。爱尔兰对欧洲的拥抱与英国形成鲜明对比，英国的经济<a href="https://cepr.org/voxeu/columns/impact-brexit-uk-economy-reviewing-evidence">仍因脱欧而陷入困境</a>。</p><p>但在投资资本方面，爱尔兰还有一张更大的王牌——美国。正如<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-polandmalaysia-model">波兰和马来西亚等</a>其他新兴发展明星一样，外国直接投资对爱尔兰经济非常重要。美国是迄今为止最大的投资来源国。这是新西兰外交和贸易部<a href="https://www.mfat.govt.nz/en/trade/mfat-market-reports/foreign-direct-investment-in-ireland-june-2023/">最近的一份报告</a>：</p><blockquote><p>按人均计算，爱尔兰是欧盟新外国直接投资 (FDI) 项目最受欢迎的目的地。自 1960 年代以来，吸引 FDI 一直是爱尔兰政府政策的基石，而 FDI 现在在支持爱尔兰经济方面发挥着非常重要的作用……</p><p>投资主要来自美国，海外的大量爱尔兰侨民帮助促进了联系。 2020年，美国对爱尔兰的直接投资达到3900亿美元，超过美国对巴西、俄罗斯、印度、中国和南非（金砖五国）的总和。尽管所有行业的投资都受到欢迎，但那些提供高价值出口产品（例如信息通信技术和制药）的行业受到青睐……</p><p>从全球分布来看，在爱尔兰投资的跨国公司中有 847 家来自美国，354 家来自欧洲，其中近一半来自德国和法国，136 家来自英国，212 家来自其他地区世界的[。]</p></blockquote><p><a href="https://www.civitas.org.uk/content/files/industrialpolicyintherepublicofireland.pdf">我读到的一份报告</a>将爱尔兰称为“硅谷和欧洲之间的中间人”。</p><p>正如报告所提到的，美国拥有大量爱尔兰侨民——约<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Irish_Americans">3600 万</a>，是爱尔兰人口的七倍多。但在美国和爱尔兰之间建立联系的不仅仅是侨民——而是侨民的<em>想法</em>。由于爱尔兰人是美国建国后第一批来到美国的外国工人，他们的故事对于美国作为一个移民国家的自我认同至关重要。许多没有爱尔兰血统的美国人喜欢想象自己有爱尔兰血统—— <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Americans_of_Irish_descent#:~:text=At%20least%2022%20presidents%20of,has%20strong%20documented%20Irish%20origins.">例如比尔·克林顿(Bill Clinton)</a> ，他声称的爱尔兰血统永远无法得到证实。每个人在圣帕特里克节都会喝醉。</p><p>这种对祖先的依恋和情感的结合显示了强大的侨民的力量。几个世纪以来，爱尔兰将<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Irish_diaspora">年轻人送往国外</a>的倾向历来被视为一种弱点。自 1990 年以来，爱尔兰一直是一个实例，说明移民如何回旋并最终成为一种力量。</p><h4>爱尔兰的政策决定了一切</h4><p>粗略地说，发展政策有三种。这些都是：</p><ul><li><p>自由化</p></li><li><p>能力建设</p></li><li><p>产业政策</p></li></ul><p>自由化只是意味着消除经济活动的障碍——高税收、监管、贸易壁垒等等。能力建设意味着投资于教育、卫生和基础设施等领域。产业政策可能有很多不同的含义，从补贴出口到吸引外国投资，再到促进特定产业发展。</p><p>对这些方法争论不休的人们写了很多文章，但当你查看开发成功案例时，你会发现它们往往都涉及其中的某些部分。爱尔兰也不例外。</p><p>爱尔兰的自由化之旅很早就开始了。即使早在 20 世纪 50 年代，当爱尔兰主要出口农产品时，其领导人<a href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/42912423">就认识到外国市场准入的重要性</a>。 20 世纪 70 年代，像<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/T._K._Whitaker">TK Whitaker</a>这样的经济政策影响者成功地主张自由贸易——如果你是一个没有太多国内市场的小国，自由贸易就至关重要。当然，欧洲经济共同体和欧盟对此至关重要。事实上，小国相对于大国的一大增长优势可能就是贸易开放性。在一个小国家，每个人都意识到国内市场是不够的。</p><p>爱尔兰的企业税率也是出了名的低，这也是爱尔兰享有避税天堂美誉的部分原因（另一部分原因是一些奇怪的税收漏洞）。但事实上，情况并非总是如此。直到 90 年代末，爱尔兰对各种企业收入都实行<em>高</em>税率，但制造业除外，制造业的税率非常低： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg" width="600" height="580" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:580,&quot;width&quot;:600,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:60359,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">作者：Britishfinance -<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=74620395">自己的作品</a>，CC BY-SA 4.0</figcaption></figure></div><p>这是自由化和产业政策的结合。制造业的优惠低利率帮助经济活动偏向于电子和制药等领域；如果没有这种分割利率，爱尔兰可能会像英国一样成为金融重镇。</p><p>事实上，人们想知道降低其他类型企业收入的税率是否可能无意中将爱尔兰投资从凯尔特老虎时期的优势转向房地产投机和避税天堂等恶作剧。但避税天堂的<a href="https://www.journals.uchicago.edu/doi/abs/10.1086/tpe.19.20061896">增长速度也往往快</a>于其他国家。部分原因可能是，许多税收制度只允许公司在实际将工厂迁往该国时才能利用该国的低税率。因此，爱尔兰可能会通过税收套利吸引企业来吸收外国技术。</p><p>部分由于低税率和其他各种有利于商业的政策，爱尔兰经常在各种“竞争力”排名中名列前茅； 2023年，它<a href="https://www.imd.org/centers/wcc/world-competitiveness-center/rankings/world-competitiveness-ranking/2023/">在IMD全球排名中排名第二</a>，仅次于丹麦，在“商业效率”和“政府效率”方面排名尤其靠前。</p><p>张夏俊 (Ha-Joon Chang) 等一些思想家对外国直接投资作为发展驱动力表示担忧。他们担心外国公司不会放弃他们最好的技术，外国品牌会排挤国内品牌，最终限制一个国家向价值链顶端的提升。爱尔兰政策制定者也有同样的担忧，<a href="https://www.civitas.org.uk/content/files/industrialpolicyintherepublicofireland.pdf">并做出了各种努力</a>来促进国内创新。到目前为止，尚不清楚这是否有效（特别是因为爱尔兰的税收恶作剧使得宏观数据难以评估）。</p><p>当然，要建设富裕的经济，你肯定需要的一件事就是大量熟练劳动力。获得熟练劳动力有两种方式——教育和移民——一般来说，你应该同时使用这两种方式。爱尔兰做到了。它的婴儿潮比其他富裕国家规模更大、持续时间更长： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg" width="1020" height="720" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:169711,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>爱尔兰在教育年轻人方面也做得很好，是经合组织中高等教育<a href="https://data.oecd.org/eduatt/population-with-tertiary-education.htm">比例最高的国家之一</a>。</p><p>但爱尔兰也引进了大量工人。 20 世纪 90 年代，传统的移民模式发生逆转，人们开始大规模移居爱尔兰： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg" width="900" height="578" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:578,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:113626,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.cso.ie/en/releasesandpublications/ep/p-pme/populationandmigrationestimatesapril2023/keyfindings/">爱尔兰 CSO</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这些移民往往偏年轻。而且他们的技能高得不成比例；到 2022 年，超过一半的爱尔兰移民<a href="https://mcginleylaw.ie/irish-immigration-statistics-2023/#:~:text=Over%2050%25%20of%20immigrants%20had,those%20seeking%20asylum%20in%20Ireland.">拥有大学学位或类似学位</a>。其中一些是<a href="https://personal.lse.ac.uk/minns/minns_jssisi_2005.pdf">自然的自我选择</a>，但爱尔兰也制定了促进技术移民的政策。</p><p>他们也来自不同的国家。爱尔兰中央统计局<a href="https://www.cso.ie/en/releasesandpublications/ep/p-pme/populationandmigrationestimatesapril2023/keyfindings/">发现，2022年</a>共有141,600名移民，其中29,600人是回国的爱尔兰公民。约26,000人来自欧盟，约42,000人来自乌克兰，4800人来自英国，约39,000人来自其他国家。</p><p>在许多国家对移民产生敌意或至少质疑其价值之际，爱尔兰总体上继续欢迎外国工人。有一些迹象表明，东欧移民<a href="https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/14782804.2022.2090321">并不像西欧和全球移民那么成功</a>，而且我在基尔肯尼逗留期间确实遇到了一些针对东欧人的刻板印象。去年，出现了<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2023/mar/21/ireland-anti-refugee-protests-far-right-uk-politics">针对难民的小规模反弹</a>。</p><p>但总体而言，爱尔兰人<a href="https://odi.org/en/publications/public-narratives-and-attitudes-towards-refugees-and-other-migrants-ireland-country-profile/">对移民的态度</a>始终比<a href="https://heartsandminds.odi.digital/country?country=ie">欧洲其他任何人都</a>更加积极。无论如何，我简短的个人经历证实了这一点。与我交谈的爱尔兰人似乎非常清楚外国工人——尤其是技术工人——对他们国家的经济崛起有多么重要。一些人提到酒吧文化和体育是文化融合的关键机制。还有人认为爱尔兰是一个“高情商国家”，其人民专门管理来自世界各地的顶尖工程师。与我交谈过的人似乎都不认为爱尔兰移民政策取得了巨大的成功。</p><p>换句话说，爱尔兰做了很多事情来试图创造经济奇迹。它放宽了贸易政策，减税，创造了有利的商业环境，并吸引了大批移民。但它也鼓励制造业，努力促进国内创新，并对教育进行大力投资。爱尔兰做到了这一切，而且不知何故，它取得了成功。</p><h4>凯尔特虎队的下一步是什么？</h4><p>毫无疑问，爱尔兰目前最大的政策挑战是住房。快速移民以及生育更替水平引发了人口激增： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg" width="913" height="576" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:576,&quot;width&quot;:913,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:65516,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.cso.ie/en/releasesandpublications/ep/p-pme/populationandmigrationestimatesapril2023/keyfindings/">爱尔兰 CSO</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>但这种繁荣<a href="https://www.irishtimes.com/ireland/housing-planning/2023/03/23/irelands-housing-crisis-facts-and-figures-all-you-need-to-know/">并没有与新住房建设的繁荣相匹配</a>。爱尔兰仍然非常热衷于单户住宅的想法；很少有人住在公寓里。该国的许可程序可能比美国<a href="https://www.thefitzwilliam.com/p/a-simple-and-elegant-response-to">还要繁琐</a>；我遇到了一些来到爱尔兰研究该国错误的 YIMBY 人。</p><p>住房经常被列为爱尔兰持续外国直接投资面临的<a href="https://www.mfat.govt.nz/en/trade/mfat-market-reports/foreign-direct-investment-in-ireland-june-2023/">最大挑战</a>，而过度拥挤可能是反移民政治最终席卷爱尔兰的原因之一。如果这个问题得不到解决，爱尔兰可能会追随<a href="https://worksinprogress.co/issue/why-britain-doesnt-build">英国的脚步陷入优雅的衰落</a>并非不可想象。</p><p>但就目前而言，爱尔兰仍然对凯尔特老虎时代的成功感到自豪。一个曾经被邻国征服和<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anti-Irish_sentiment">蔑视的</a>国家现在成为财富和高科技技能的灯塔。</p><p>我认为这给我们上了关于国家发展的重要一课。如果你回到 1923 年，问人们一百年后爱尔兰是否会比英国更富有，你认为有多少人会回答“是”？有多少人会当面嘲笑你？然而一个世纪后，我们却来到了这里，这就是现实。现在拿出一张世界地图，选出一些大多数人认为不具备致富条件的国家。您认为 100 年后这些国家会在哪里？</p><p>你确定吗？ </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-ireland-got-so-rich?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-ireland-got-so-rich?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p>; 
The Middle East is getting olderWhy I'm optimistic about the waning of conflict in the region. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-middle-east-is-getting-older https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-middle-east-is-getting-olderNoah Smith Sun, 05 Nov 2023 02:16:18 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg" width="1024" height="768" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:768,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:519992,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption">作者： <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=17138401">Syria-Frames-Of-Freedom</a> （支持 FSA 的信息）- [1]，CC BY 2.0</figcaption></figure></div><p>我注意到以色列-加沙战争中一些有趣的事情似乎普遍被忽视了：战争并没有显示出太多蔓延到整个中东的迹象。也门胡塞武装（伊朗的傀儡民兵组织之一）向以色列的大致方向发射了几枚导弹，并<a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/features/2023/11/2/analysis-houthis-declare-war-on-israel-but-their-real-target-is-elsewhere">大声宣战</a>，但似乎没有人很担心。 2006年，黎巴嫩民兵真主党与以色列的战斗陷入僵局，但现在<a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/world-news/2023/11/03/hassan-nasrallah-hezbollah-speech-oct-7-hamas-iran-israel/">它选择不介入</a>这场冲突，伊朗本身也是如此。早在2000年代初期，每个人都害怕的“阿拉伯街道”肯定有支持巴勒斯坦人的抗议活动，但<a href="https://carnegieendowment.org/2023/11/01/pay-attention-to-arab-public-response-to-israel-hamas-war-pub-90893">他们一直非常和平</a>。沙特阿拉伯表示，<a href="https://www.axios.com/2023/10/31/saudi-megadeal-normalization-israel-biden">仍希望与以色列实现关系正常化</a>，但以停火为条件。</p><p>这是一个非常好的迹象，与战争最初几天大家所抱有的可怕期望相去甚远。 2011年，“阿拉伯之春”如野火般蔓延，引发了叙利亚和也门大规模、漫长的血腥战争，以及整个中东地区的各种小规模战争；以色列-加沙战争没有任何迹象表明这段历史会重演。</p><p>当然，这可能有很多原因。经过二十年的战争，该地区可能已经筋疲力尽。<a href="https://taskandpurpose.com/news/two-navy-aircraft-carriers-mediterranean/">美国的威慑</a>可能正在限制伊朗及其代理人的手。对于该地区来说，以巴冲突可能根本不如伊朗和沙特阿拉伯之间的长期冷战那么重要。 ETC。</p><p>但我认为人口老龄化也可能与此有关。有相当成熟的文献将年轻人口膨胀与冲突风险升高联系起来。当然，这种联系只是一种相关性——除了战争本身之外，显然很难找到改变一个国家年龄结构的自然实验。但这是一个相当明确的相关性。例如， <a href="https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-030-73065-9_3">Cincotta 和 Weber (2021)</a>发现，年龄中位数为 25 岁或以下的国家更有可能发生革命： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg" width="668" height="460.16157205240177" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:631,&quot;width&quot;:916,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:668,&quot;bytes&quot;:79076,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-030-73065-9_3">Cincotta 和 Weber (2021)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p> <a href="https://academic.oup.com/isq/article/50/3/607/1800827?login=false">Urdal (2006)</a>发现：</p><blockquote><p>人们经常认为……所谓的“青年膨胀”使国家更容易受到政治暴力的影响……这一说法在 1950 年至 2000 年期间国内武装冲突的时间序列跨国统计模型中得到了实证检验，以及 1984-1995 年恐怖主义和骚乱的事件数据。所有三种形式的暴力都强烈支持年轻人激增会增加政治暴力风险的预期。</p></blockquote><p><a href="https://www.cfr.org/report/family-planning-strategic-focus-us-foreign-policy">马德森（2021）</a>写道：</p><blockquote><p> 20 世纪 90 年代的证据表明，15 至 29 岁人口占成年人口 40% 以上的国家，遭受内战的可能性是其他国家的两倍。 1970 年至 2007 年间，80% 的国内冲突爆发发生在至少 60% 的人口年龄在 30 岁以下的国家……这些国家中只有少数国家被评为民主国家，并且对政治自由、腐败和腐败等问题进行了限制。机构能力薄弱也很常见。从 1950 年到 2000 年收集的数据发现，那些 35% 或以上成年人口由 15 岁到 24 岁的人组成的国家，爆发内战的可能性要高出 150%。在生育率持续较高的国家，这种相关性最强。一旦人口转变完全开始，尽管由于过去高生育率带来的人口动力，人口仍然年轻，但爆发冲突的可能性较小。</p></blockquote><p> <a href="https://erf.org.eg/app/uploads/2019/06/1310.pdf">Ibrahim (2019)</a>和其他人也发现了类似的结果。一如既往，<a href="https://www.newsecuritybeat.org/2018/04/age-structure-intra-state-conflict-imagined/">该理论存在批评者</a>，一些作者根据不同类型的冲突进行了区分——例如， <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Dan-Miodownik/publication/265650970_Youth_bulge_and_civil_war_Why_a_country's_share_of_young_adults_explains_only_non-ethnic_wars/links/5ad50cf9a6fdcc2935809baa/Youth-bulge-and-civil-war-Why-a-countrys-share-of-young-adults-explains-only-non-ethnic-wars.pdf">Yair 和 Midownik (2014)</a>声称青年膨胀与“种族战争”不太相关，而 Cincotta 和 Weber (2021) ）警告说，他们的结果更难测试“分裂主义”战争。但无论如何，该领域的普遍共识似乎是，非常年轻的人口与不稳定和暴力有关。</p><p>关于为何青年人激增可能引发冲突，有多种理论。资源稀缺是非常贫穷国家的一个明显因素。在其他国家，有一种理论认为，年轻人的激增会导致年轻人的经济和社会机会减少——基本上，年轻人互相排挤，这让他们生气。当经济停滞时，这种效应显然会加剧。此外，身边有很多年轻人而没有什么可失去的，这本身就是一个风险因素。</p><p>中东停滞的经济显然是席卷整个地区的暴力事件的一个因素（当然，这显然是双向的因果关系）。无论富裕还是贫穷，大中东地区的国家——我会把阿富汗和巴基斯坦也包括在内，因为它们也是冲突的重灾区——就是根本不会经历太多的经济增长。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg" width="684" height="490.8705882352941" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWaterm