在历史低点附近。 - 年龄就业率<a href="https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/LNS12300060">接近历史最高水平</a>，接近 81%。通货膨胀率已大幅下降，目前<a href="https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/CPIAUCSL">约为 3.7%</a> ，核心通货膨胀<a href="https://twitter.com/jasonfurman/status/1718257239817925078">率略低</a>，<a href="https://www.atlantafed.org/chcs/wage-growth-tracker">工资中位数增长</a>速度超过了通货膨胀率。与此同时，新的调查数据显示，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/great-news-about-american-wealth">美国人变得更加富有</a>，财富不平等有所缩小。</p></blockquote><p>但我在写该部分时注意到一条有趣的推文： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa911a25f-ef8d-4247-be6c-00dc7701ea2d_911x246.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa911a25f-ef8d-4247-be6c-00dc7701ea2d_911x246.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa911a25f-ef8d-4247-be6c-00dc7701ea2d_911x246.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa911a25f-ef8d-4247-be6c-00dc7701ea2d_911x246.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa911a25f-ef8d-4247-be6c-00dc7701ea2d_911x246.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa911a25f-ef8d-4247-be6c-00dc7701