ome-net-exporter-crude-oil-2023-2022-12-19/">原油净出口国</a>。沙特阿拉伯、阿联酋和科威特可能会被哥斯拉吃掉，而我们的炼油厂将继续运转。 （顺便说一句，拜登领导下的美国石油产量<a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/08/09/business/oil-production-biden-trump/index.html">刚刚创下新纪录</a>。）</p><p>现在，我们的一些盟友，比如日本和韩国，确实仍然购买了大量中东石油。如果中东石油供应出现严重中断，全球石油价格将大幅上涨，为美国石油生产商带来意外之财，但也会损害美国其他类型的企业。但<a href="https://about.bnef.com/blog/electric-cars-have-dented-fuel-demand-by-2040-theyll-slash-it/">由于电动汽车的兴起</a>，石油对全球经济的重要性日益降低。预计石油总消耗量很快就会持平。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg" width="655" he