"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>现在，也许杰森只是从他自己的经济角度进行了过度推断——<a href="https://twitter.com/zachcoelius/status/1715800756333453823">科技初创公司正在遭受苦难</a>，因为他们在 2022 年经济崩溃之前筹集的现金已经耗尽且无法替代。但事实上，现在很多美国人都在对经济发表非常负面的言论。尽管有所有经济好消息，但消费者信心<a href="https://twitter.com/crampell/status/1717904753047319030">仍然低迷</a>。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F29c582fe-d05c-415c-b9da-377d0ded400a_1318x450.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F29c582fe-d05c-415c-b9da-377d0ded400a_1318x450.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F29c582fe-d05c-415c-b9da-377d0ded400a_1318x450.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F29c582fe-d05c-415c-b9da-377d0ded400a_1318x450.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F29c582fe-d05c-415c-b9da-377d0ded400a_1318x450.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F29c582fe-d05c-415c-b9da-377d0ded400a_1318x450.jpeg" width="1318" height="450" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/publi